title: Mick Jagger - Out Of Focus (cd single) 192kbps
description:
************************************
I got my good old trusty box with my old cds from my mothers attic and thought to myself - maybe there's some fun stuff to share. I did not see this on tpb, but quite frankly I did not look that hard.

Mick Jagger - Out Of Focus (CD single from the album "Wandering Spirit" from 1993)

it contains:

1. Out Of Focus (7" Hipgrass)
2. Out Of Focus (Album Version)
3. Out Of Focus (12" Hipgrass)
4. Out Of Focus (12" Whatstax Dub)

Note that if you ever seen the music video for Out Of Focus, it is actually the 7" Hipgrass version and not the album version (easy to tell the difference). If you've ever been wanting "that video version" (for some reason or another) you are in luck - because here it is. Freshly ripped in 192kbps LAME, joint stereo.

I'll probably find both my "Sweet Thing" singles soon as well. Completists rejoice.

Enjoy
